# Written by Maks Inkster

<title>About Us:</title>
<p>With over 20 locations across Scotland, we are the biggest animal rescue charity in the country</p>
<img>Cute photo of a dog</img>
<p>Founded by Odin McKenzie in 1993, we've been taking in animals across the nation for the last 30 years, taking care of them and finding them new homes</p>
<video>Pet Sanctuary Tour.mp4</video>
<p>Our Sancturies have space for over 200 animals, and we've taken in over 500 unique animals across our history</p>
